e":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拖長黎夾硬畫落去 好心作者好頭好尾快d完q左佢啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴應該算係所有童話故事最強商人<br />\n<del>撇除耶穌開外掛五餅二魚同將水變走</del><br />\n<br />\n我想睇商會繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed28d0070f030ff2989f08386060133c5550a108","tid":25412,"uid":396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正常黎講<br />\n<br />\n摩兒個種族根本唔屬於依家所羅生創造出黎果個世界既<br />\n<br />\n即係重寫洗腦rufu根本唔會關摩兒事,就同果條原始龍一樣<br />\n<br />\n但依家又寫到摩兒都俾人洗埋腦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁講穆同埋馬斯魯爾都唔會有事啦<br />\n唔知佢會點吹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢最尾果格係摩兒應該有d野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但摩兒係峽谷另一面有一段時間修練"},{"pid":"7ce6e4e34947ac21c26fc52167b7edadffc41cdb","tid":25412,"uid":396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"或者會唔會因為摩兒同阿里巴巴感情上有牽絆，所以睇直播時洗腦慢慢消除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b90451284cc73065201c5dcc44e80e710d2c88","tid":25412,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者會唔會因為摩兒同阿里巴巴感情上有牽絆，所以睇直播時洗腦慢慢消除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照計法納利斯應該冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9cb07ac3c780b826b01b27fdf3c960751e6f29","tid":25412,"uid":40771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:04:10.000Z","msg":"吹水有乜好睇<br />\n成套野淨係睇魔裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b5c2e3758b5b8247bac4b29a807b15d11579a5","tid":25412,"uid":33987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"摩兒好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55e78f3acb2717513a0656c4d432be024b356a0","tid":25412,"uid":51300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:01:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>或者會唔會因為摩兒同阿里巴巴感情上有牽絆，所以睇直播時洗腦慢慢消除<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n照計法納利斯應該冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我一直都唔明，之前換世界的時候，將所有的種族都變晒人樣，靜係紅獅同原始龍變唔到，既然係咁法納利斯又點解可以係人樣？？"},{"pid":"9f302802f0c5acc5f8d7c63f9dc2d1bdee19d425","tid":25412,"uid":51300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正常黎講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n摩兒個種族根本唔屬於依家所羅生創造出黎果個世界既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係重寫洗腦rufu根本唔會關摩兒事,就同果條原始龍一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但依家又寫到摩兒都俾人洗埋腦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁講穆同埋馬斯魯爾都唔會有事啦<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會點吹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢最尾果格係摩兒應該有d野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但摩兒係峽谷另一面有一段時間修練</blockquote><br />\n佢一早變返紅獅LA，係阿拉丁將佢變返做人型。<br />\n可能經過呢個PROCESS，佢唔會好似其他法納利斯咁。"},{"pid":"aaba13a6c6e8a792b868b2149bd96515e325304d","tid":25412,"uid":5420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正常黎講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n摩兒個種族根本唔屬於依家所羅生創造出黎果個世界既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係重寫洗腦rufu根本唔會關摩兒事,就同果條原始龍一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但依家又寫到摩兒都俾人洗埋腦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁講穆同埋馬斯魯爾都唔會有事啦<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會點吹</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢最尾果格係摩兒應該有d野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但摩兒係峽谷另一面有一段時間修練</blockquote><br />\n佢一早變返紅獅LA，係阿拉丁將佢變返做人型。<br />\n可能經過呢個PROCESS，佢唔會好似其他法納利斯咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾時有變返紅獅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hk