S，佢唔會好似其他法納利斯咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾時有變返紅獅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最終章開始之後，講阿拉丁同摩兒係峽谷另一面有一段時間修練果陣，有講過佢變過紅獅。"},{"pid":"3632c63859fcedc7f42b090204cdc171df1a7517","tid":25412,"uid":7585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"人類補完計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea04164e039b7d6bbbb22934d43605196eb29707","tid":25412,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:16:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;正常黎講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n摩兒個種族根本唔屬於依家所羅生創造出黎果個世界既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係重寫洗腦rufu根本唔會關摩兒事,就同果條原始龍一樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但依家又寫到摩兒都俾人洗埋腦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁講穆同埋馬斯魯爾都唔會有事啦<br />\n<br />\n唔知佢會點吹&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢最尾果格係摩兒應該有d野&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但摩兒係峽谷另一面有一段時間修練&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n佢一早變返紅獅LA，係阿拉丁將佢變返做人型。<br />\n可能經過呢個PROCESS，佢唔會好似其他法納利斯咁。&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n幾時有變返紅獅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全部係人樣呢條法則淨係會係非黑暗大陸既地方生效<br />\n即係係紅獅子都好，離開黑暗大陸就會被呢條法則所束縛<br />\n所以洗腦理論上其實對唔係黑暗大陸既摩兒都係有效<br />\n好似係咁</blockquote><br />\n但係黑暗大陸應該係under所羅門唔係烏戈 辛巴德應該洗唔到所羅門既rufu"},{"pid":"b47614b20cebb66d6e7faa94cf0ba9b3a0315c82","tid":25412,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"食撚屎啦 吹撚到辛巴德勁到實力無上限咁"},{"pid":"8dc6436e11d7c665f5f566d9e91b253e4617768c","tid":25412,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食撚屎啦